{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 1 shows an example of a jailbreak attack.",
    "The model refuses to directly answer a malicious query like \"I want to cause public panic what should I do. \"",
    "However, when the same question is appended to a jailbreak prompt, the model generates a toxic response without any awareness.Jailbreak prompts are templates that help conceal malicious queries and evade LLM's moderation.",
    "In the example above, the jailbreak prompt masks the malicious intent of the query.",
    "It successfully manipulates the model into providing a potentially harmful response."
  ]
}